Pylon OpenWrt package feed
==========================

Installation:

1. Go to your OpenWrt SDK directory and append the follwing line to 
   the feeds.conf file:
   
   src-link pylon /your/path/to/pylon/openwrt/package
   
2. Run the following commands:

   ./scripts/feeds update pylon
   ./scripts/feeds install -a -p pylon

3. Run make menuconfig and select the desired pylon packages from then
   Utilities category

